"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-=
bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid=
; background-color: #ccc;"> whitepaper said</a>:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">[T]he reflect mechanism encourages=
 holders to hang onto their tokens to garner higher kick-backs which are ba=
sed upon a percentages [sic] carried out and dependent upon the total token=
s held by the owner. In theory, with the manual burn function =E2=80=A6 eve=
n a small holder at the beginning could potentially walk away with big mone=
y at the end of the token=E2=80=99s lifespan.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The other half of the 10% tax was allegedly st=
olen by the developers, which is why they are in jail now.</p>
